<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.6">
<l>miṉṉi ṉaṉṉa nuṇmaruṅkul vēyēy taṭantōḷ melliyaṟkā</l>
<l>maṉṉu ciṉatta maḻaviṭaika ḷēḻaṉ ṟaṭartta mālatiṭam</l>
<l>maṉṉu mutunī raravinta malarmēl varivaṇ ṭicaipāṭa</l>
<l>puṉṉai poṉṉēy tātutirkkum puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of Māl who once attacked seven angry young bulls of constant rage</l>
<l>For the sake of a tender-natured [girl] with long bamboo-like arms</l>
<l rend="indent">and a lightning-like, delicate waist,</l>
<l>Is Puḷḷampūtankuṭi where laurel pollen falls like gold,</l>
<l>As striped bees sing melodies on the lotus flowers</l>
<l rend="indent">in the enduring flooded fields.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
